text: Barsat is a town located near Kaimla in the Karnal district of Haryana, India. The town is part of a region known for its rich agricultural heritage and cultural significance. == Notable People == * Samarth Kaimliya, Indian Actor and YouTuber from Kaimla * Balraj Panwar, Indian Rower from Kaimla Category:Towns in India Category:Settlements in Haryana
title: Barsat
